        "searchField": "camberinterpreter tristan-huber given a json file from the camber boat design tool generate a panelized version of the same boat hull. camber link: https://risingtideresearch.github.io/camber/index.html project",
        "owner": "tristan-huber",
        "description": "Given a JSON file from the camber boat design tool generate a panelized version of the same boat hull. camber link: https://risingtideresearch.github.io/camber/index.html",
